        <abstract> 
<p>JM states he will publish [<hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>] on same basis as <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>, i.e., paying CD two-thirds of the profits.</p>  
<p>In response to Asa Gray’s suggestion, he could supply Ticknor &amp; Fields with 250 copies [of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>, 4th ed.] at half-price.</p> 
        </abstract>
